<div class="jumbotron">
    <h2>Welcome to your Web API web service!</h2>
    <p class="lead">Your new Web API web service + Reusable Framework powered by Genesys Source is ready!</p>
    <blockquote>
        <table>
            <tr>
                <td style="width:8%;vertical-align:top;"><strong>Step 1:</strong></td>
                <td>
                    Publish the Foundation.Database (SSDT) project to your SQL Server by:
                    <ul>
                        <li>Double-click Foundation.Database\Publish\<strong>PublishToDev.publish.xml</strong> to bring up the Publish form</li>
                        <li>Set your SQL connection by clicking the <strong>Edit</strong> button</li>
                        <li>Click <strong>Publish</strong> and SSDT will publish schema, SPs, views and data to your destination database</li>
                    </ul>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td style="width:8%;vertical-align:top;"><strong>Step 2:</strong></td>
                <td>
                    Set the Foundation.Entity (EF) connection strings to your SQL Server by:
                    <ul>
                        <li>Open Foundation.WebServices\App_Data\<strong>ConnectionStrings.config</strong></li>
                        <li>Change DatabaseServer.dev.GenesysFramework.com to your SQL Server machine name</li>
                        <li>For SQL Authentication, change "Integrated Security=true" to "user id=USER; password=PASS;"</li>
                    </ul>
                    <em>Important: Most problems are caused by invalid SQL Connection and/or User</em>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td style="width:8%;vertical-align:top;"><strong>Step 3: </strong></td>
                <td>
                    Run the Foundation.WebServices project!
                    <ul>
                        <li>Right-cick the <strong>Foundation.WebServices</strong> project and select <strong>Set as Startup Project</strong></li>
                        <li>Press <strong>F5</strong> to run</li>
                        <li>Type the following path to display customer 18 data: <strong>/v1/customer/18</strong></li>
                    </ul>
                </td>
            </tr>
        </table>
    </blockquote>
    <p><a href="http://docs.GenesysFramework.com/library/Genesys-Foundation-Quick-Guide.pdf" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">View Foundation Starter-Kit Guide &raquo;</a></p>
</div>

